code: @Override public String toString() {     return "option:" + getOptionName() + "=" + getExpression(). }

comment: /**  * Name of the option. It identifies the name of the header where the value of the expression will be stored when the  * compensation or completion routes will be called.  */
code: /**  * Name of the option. It identifies the name of the header where the value of the expression will be stored when the  * compensation or completion routes will be called.  */ public void setOptionName(String optionName) {     this.optionName = optionName. }

comment: /**  * The expression to be used to determine the value of the option.  */
code: /**  * The expression to be used to determine the value of the option.  */ public void setExpression(ExpressionDefinition expression) {     this.expression = expression. }
